|text2     = While in "Black Tide Fever," targets receive Wind Shear, Burn, Shock, and Bleed DoT at the start of every turn.
|image3    = Tutorial Black Tide Fever 3.png{{subst:void|<!--$UPLOAD:<<SpriteOutput/TutorialPic/TutorialPage_224503.png>-<Tutorial Black Tide Fever 3.png>-<Tutorial Files>>-->}}
|text3     = The enemies' "Black Tide Fever" is immediately dispelled when the "Revel in Destruction" state ends. Allies' "Black Tide Fever" is immediately dispelled when their HP is fully restored. Units will not take the DoT damage after this state is dispelled.
